text.tspan: LET IT BE KNOW THAT ON THE DAY OF , 20

flowRoot.flowPara: Entered a battle of the bots and their robot "lawyer," a rudimentary housing issue spotter was found to be the best "bot" as judged by F1 Score. Consequently, they are entitled to appropriate bragging rights, including but not limited to, social media posting of themselves with this certificate tagged #LegalTech #FTW.
